Class QuadTreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ajgl.primary.Drawable
      • org.ajgl.primary.GameObject
        • org.ajgl.collision.QuadTreeNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Collidable, ConvexPolygon, Polygon

    public class QuadTreeNode
extends GameObject
    This class is designed to to act as a QuadTree node and should not be extended unless necessary.
    Author:
    Tyler Bucher
